WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:03.703 align:start size:88% position:13% line:0%
- Hello beloved drones,
and welcome to the

00:00:03.703 --> 00:00:04.938 line:0%
Seven Million Habits
of Highly Effective

00:00:04.938 --> 00:00:06.372 line:0%
Hampton Deville Employees.

00:00:06.372 --> 00:00:08.707 line:0%
- Habit number 835,
dress for the job

00:00:08.707 --> 00:00:11.043 line:0%
you want, not the job you have.

00:00:11.043 --> 00:00:12.244 line:0%
- Find the person
whose job you want

00:00:12.244 --> 00:00:13.946
and dress exactly like them.

00:00:13.946 --> 00:00:16.181
- I got my job by dressing
like Kate for two weeks.

00:00:16.181 --> 00:00:17.383
- And I pretended to be a man.

00:00:17.383 --> 00:00:18.450
- But don't just
dress like them,

00:00:18.450 --> 00:00:19.919
you should act like them, too.

00:00:19.919 --> 00:00:21.187
- Walk like them.

00:00:21.187 --> 00:00:22.421
- Move your arms
around like them.

00:00:22.421 --> 00:00:23.689
- Follow them around
with a tape recorder

00:00:23.689 --> 00:00:24.590
to record their
voice in meetings

00:00:24.590 --> 00:00:25.558
or on the phone, even at home.

00:00:25.558 --> 00:00:26.759
- Follow them home.

00:00:26.759 --> 00:00:27.560 align:start size:84% position:16%
- Steal their credit
card information.

00:00:27.560 --> 00:00:28.527
- Drive their car.

00:00:28.527 --> 00:00:29.295
- Kiss their children goodnight.

00:00:29.295 --> 00:00:30.096
- Sleep with their wife.

00:00:30.096 --> 00:00:31.297
- And their husband.

00:00:31.297 --> 00:00:32.465 align:start size:84% position:16%
- That's right,
they're polyamorous.

00:00:32.465 --> 00:00:33.733 align:start size:84% position:16%
- Why did you
assume they weren't?

00:00:33.733 --> 00:00:35.235
- Let go of whatever
preconceived notions

00:00:35.235 --> 00:00:36.436 align:start size:94% position:6%
you have about what a
relationship is or can be.

00:00:36.436 --> 00:00:37.937 align:start size:84% position:16%
- It is the 21st
century, god damn it.

00:00:37.937 --> 00:00:41.808
- And before you know it,
you'll have their job.

